CREATE TABLE `doc-ai-studio.qsight_test.LoanedBorrowed`
(
  LoanedBorrowedId STRING NOT NULL,
  DepartmentId STRING NOT NULL,
  ProductVariantId STRING NOT NULL,
  RecipientId STRING NOT NULL,
  DateDue TIMESTAMP,
  DateReturned TIMESTAMP,
  Quantity INT64 NOT NULL,
  Inactive BOOL NOT NULL,
  InventoryTransactionId STRING,
  Note STRING(3000),
  DateCreated TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  DateLastModified TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
)
PARTITION BY DATE(DateCreated);
